Package org.eclipse.microprofile.openapi.models.responses

Interface APIResponses

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Constructible, Extensible<APIResponses>, java.util.Map<java.lang.String,APIResponse>

    public interface APIResponses
extends Constructible, Extensible<APIResponses>, java.util.Map<java.lang.String,APIResponse>
    This interface represents the container for the expected responses of an operation. The container maps a HTTP response code to the expected response.
    See Also:
